{
  "text": "The synthetic dataset in table 5.1 (taken from ref. [CITATION_1] . So, only Doc1 and Doc3 are retrieved, and Doc2 is lost. Similarly, if a query containing {colour} is made, then only Doc4 will be retrieved, and Doc5 will be lost (note that even though purple and colour can have different meanings, according to this example they are highly related, thus any query containing either one of them is expected to retrieve Doc4 and Doc5).",
